## Part 1: Persistent Volumes & Claims (PV/PVC) 💾

### 1. HostPath Setup & PV/PVC Creation

We created a local directory on the host to serve as storage, added an `index.html` file with the student's name, and created a Persistent Volume (1GB, Recycle policy) along with its corresponding Persistent Volume Claim.

```bash
# Setup HostPath
sudo mkdir -p /opt/nginx-data
echo "Mohamed Mostafa Nada" | sudo tee /opt/nginx-data/index.html

# Apply PV and PVC
sudo kubectl apply -f pv-pvc.yaml
sudo kubectl get pv,pvc
```

