### 2. Deployment with Pod Affinity

We created a 3-replica Nginx deployment that mounts the PVC. To ensure all replicas can access the hostPath volume, we used podAffinity to schedule them all on the exact same node.

```bash
sudo kubectl apply -f pv-deploy.yaml
sudo kubectl get pods -o wide
curl http://<POD_IP>
```

