## Part 2: Downward API ⬇️

We created a deployment that dynamically injects the Pod's Name and Pod's IP into its environment variables using the Kubernetes Downward API. These values are then written to the index.html file upon container startup.

```bash
sudo kubectl apply -f downward-api.yaml
sudo kubectl get pods -o wide | grep downward
curl http://<POD_IP>
```

